      <title>欧洲复兴开发银行称今年可能向乌克兰投资 15 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ebrd-says-it-may-invest-1-5-billion-in-ukraine-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于俄罗斯的持续入侵继续对乌克兰造成破坏，欧洲复兴开发银行预计未来一年对乌克兰的投资将达到 15 亿欧元（15.4 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ebrd-says-it-may-invest-1-5-billion-in-ukraine-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>能量饮料制造商 Eastroc 即将与摩根士丹利和瑞银合作在香港上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/energy-drink-maker-eastroc-closing-on-morgan-stanley-ubs-for-hong-kong-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国能量饮料制造商东鹏饮料集团股份有限公司即将聘请摩根士丹利和瑞银集团等银行协助其在香港进行二次上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/energy-drink-maker-eastroc-closing-on-morgan-stanley-ubs-for-hong-kong-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 05:51:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
