      <title>加沙协议影响运费，亚洲船舶库存下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/asian-shipper-stocks-slide-as-gaza-deal-weighs-on-freight-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预期以色列与哈马斯达成的停火协议将使红海航运恢复正常，导致高涨的集装箱运费下降并影响利润，亚洲航运公司的股价周四下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/asian-shipper-stocks-slide-as-gaza-deal-weighs-on-freight-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 04:22:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管央行注资，中国现金紧缩局面仍在持续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/china-cash-squeeze-rolls-on-even-after-pboc-liquidity-boosts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于北京方面注入的流动性未能抵消资金需求的激增，中国的现金紧缩状况持续，并出现一些交易中断的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/china-cash-squeeze-rolls-on-even-after-pboc-liquidity-boosts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 04:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
