      <title>美联储路径担忧缓解 比特币逼近 10 万美元大关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/bitcoin-btc-tops-100-000-mark-as-angst-over-fed-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国通胀数据利好提振，全球市场重新燃起对美联储进一步降息的押注，比特币创下新年最大涨幅，目前徘徊在 10 万美元附近。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/bitcoin-btc-tops-100-000-mark-as-angst-over-fed-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 00:14:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际能源署对俄罗斯减产发出警告且库存下降，油价维持涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-16</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对全球供应风险的担忧日益加剧，且美国商业原油库存出现 2021 年以来最长的连续下降，油价年初大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-16</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 23:31:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
